# PDF Rendering Service

## Build

    $ mvn build

## Run

    $ java -jar target/pdfairy-1.0.jar --host <host> --port <port> --threads <threadsNumber>

## Use

First save XML and XSLT documents, then run:

    $ echo '{"xml":"/path/to.xml","xsl":"/path/to.xsl","pdf":"/path/to.pdf"}' | nc <host> <port>
